How to run the project

// PORT = 8080
// MAKE SURE TO CREATE A backend/uploads folder before running on your local system
// ELSE DOCKER WILL CREATE THAT IN ITS CONTAINER
for the GO server...
RUN: cd backend
RUN: docker build -t backend-app .
RUN: docker run -p 8080:8080 backend-app 

// PORT = 8000
for python server..
RUN: python mock.py



for the frontend server...
RUN: npx serve -p 5500

// These steps are taken to prevent the default function of the live server VSCode
// extension to reload the page on every POST request
